trans-unit.source: Represents the resolution supported by a printer.
trans-unit.target: A nyomtató által támogatott felbontást jelöli.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to get the printer resolutions that are available on the printer and to set the printing resolution for a page, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Ez az osztály által használt a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>és <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Tulajdonságok állnak rendelkezésre a nyomtató nyomtató megoldásaikat, és a nyomtatási felbontás lap, illetve beállítása.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> property to determine whether the printer resolution type is the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> value <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>tulajdonság a nyomtató megoldástípus <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>érték <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> meghatározásához</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>

trans-unit.source: If so, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> properties to determine the printer resolution in the horizontal and vertical directions, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Ha igen, használja a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>és <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A>tulajdonságait határozza meg a nyomtató felbontása a vízszintes és függőleges irányban, illetve.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information on printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Nyomtatással kapcsolatos további információkért lásd: a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>névtér áttekintése.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: `dmPrintQuality` is a member of the `DEVMODE` (device mode) structure, which defines constants that map to printer quality settings.
trans-unit.target: `dmPrintQuality`tagja az `DEVMODE` definiálja a minőségi nyomtatóbeállításokat leképezése állandókat (eszköz mód) struktúrában.

trans-unit.source: The X property contains the value `DMRES_HIGH` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, and `DMRES_DRAFT` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: Az X tulajdonság értéke `DMRES_HIGH` Ha <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>értéke <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` Ha <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>értékre van állítva <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` Ha <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>értékre van állítva <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, és `DMRES_DRAFT` Ha <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> értéke</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>
